{"tid":1115183,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民公投]一個你鐘意既人同一個鐘意你既人","createTime":"2019-04-19T04:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T09:59:48.000Z","uid":224007,"like":25,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"28957477b237a8d9e7ef51bf87bcfe267c7cce9a","tid":1115183,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"假設有兩個人，<br />\n一個係你好鐘意既但佢唔鐘意你<br />\n另外一個係鐘意你但你當佢只係朋友，<br />\n應該點揀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />努力去追自己鐘意個個 總有日打動到既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />接受鐘意自己個個 可能會日久生情"},{"pid":"6ec020492c1845014490ecb5e9bc8f77802d2a15","tid":1115183,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"順便講下理由"},{"pid":"fdbb57f65d3153ece00722070309d1cafe51e0d5","tid":1115183,"uid":95637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"被愛比愛人幸福"},{"pid":"65d25c71f870ed461a7fb8975524611741d3c853","tid":1115183,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"等一個你鍾意而對方都鍾意你嘅人"},{"pid":"887f3f0725dff15e3ebfd2f19ec06f7942397154","tid":1115183,"uid":87781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"始終 愛意你既人會考慮埋你感受！"},{"pid":"9ed823ff21fc18496b91848ec92de049936ea774","tid":1115183,"uid":87781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"887f3f0725dff15e3ebfd2f19ec06f7942397154","tid":1115183,"uid":87781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"始終 愛意你既人會考慮埋你感受！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"鐘意"},{"pid":"a35a14de3e114ee42b4c0f9ab94caac250da1bdd","tid":1115183,"uid":87781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"唔洗太多顧慮 <br />\n利申:絲打"},{"pid":"6a71dec8121efba28e76976362eaf254f6c2bed5","tid":1115183,"uid":188148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:24:42.000Z","msg":"緊係接受鐘意自己個<br />\n雖然鐘意我既女人都唔方靚得去邊<br />\n但真人覺得比人鐘意相處會好d"},{"pid":"f1215a0a61e7de48983e7bb036a5a5477548f9ac","tid":1115183,"uid":63692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"憑空FF會答鍾意自己嘅人<br />\n到真係有得揀嘅時候就唔會咁諗"},{"pid":"aa6418bddcb665e2c968bd1f282bd4d76ca67913","tid":1115183,"uid":187544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"簡單例子<br />\n你鐘意既人 - 法拉<br />\n鐘意你既人 - 欣宜<br />\n<br />\n考慮因素：<br />\n你追法拉難度同改變自己去接受欣宜難度邊個易。<br />\n<br />\n追法拉 - 決定權係法拉度，即係你被動，沒話事權。<br />\n接受欣宜 - 決定權係自己度，你認為接受到，件事就解決。<br />\n<br />\n從決定權角度，只要大權在握，事情一般都比較易辦，一旦大權在別人，那就要看別人態度。"},{"pid":"1b0a6ced6ba5e08a7d45a0cf127853cd771ea4cc","tid":1115183,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdbb57f65d3153ece00722070309d1cafe51e0d5","tid":1115183,"uid":95637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"被愛比愛人幸福"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"但如果揀左後者 但成日都諗住自己鐘意個個 會唔會對後者太慘"},{"pid":"b9389919b24e7265dc84aa1bb1ab4316afce1c80","tid":1115183,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0a6ced6ba5e08a7d45a0cf127853cd771ea4cc","tid":1115183,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdbb57f65d3153ece00722070309d1cafe51e0d5","tid":1115183,"uid":95637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"被愛比愛人幸福"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"但如果揀左後者 但成日都諗住自己鐘意個個 會唔會對後者太慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"得到個人得唔到個心咁"},{"pid":"90d94f6dea8a0fe61d5b4e81c8468fc7ab1a313c","tid":1115183,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0a6ced6ba5e08a7d45a0cf127853cd771ea4cc","tid":1115183,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdbb57f65d3153ece00722070309d1cafe51e0d5","tid":1115183,"uid":95637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"sc